title: Alienoil - In Limbo - dark electro, industrial, goth
description:
Artist: Alienoil
Album: In Limbo
Year: 2013
Label: Halotan Records
Genre: dark electro, industrial, goth, female vocals

Intriguing sound, professional production, excellent female vocals and lots of space - these are the strongest points of this release. The style is electro industrial and most of the songs have medium to slow tempo, so this is not a club oriented music.

More info: http://www.halotan.net
